# ============================================================================
# NOTES
# ============================================================================
# 
# This .gitignore file covers:
# - Backend: .NET 9 build artifacts, Visual Studio files
# - Frontend: Angular build, node_modules, dist
# - Docker: configuration persistence
# - Environment: local configs, secrets, sensitive data
# - IDE: All major IDEs (VS, VSCode, Rider, Sublime, etc.)
# - OS: Windows, macOS, Linux artifacts
# - Build: Temporary build and cache files
#
# Important:
# - Never commit: .env files, secrets, passwords, API keys
# - Never commit: Local IDE configurations (unless team agreement)
# - Always commit: docker-compose.yml, Dockerfile, documentation
# - Always commit: package.json, tsconfig.json, .editorconfig
#
# For more patterns: https://github.com/github/gitignore
# ============================================================================
